# ds4.env — ds4-server configuration (this file IS the config surface).
#
# Seeded to /opt/data/ds4.env on first start and NEVER overwritten — your edits
# here win. Sourced by the droste entrypoint; the port's PRE_LAUNCH translates
# the DS4_DROSTE_* vars into ds4-server flags (ds4 has no native per-flag env).
#
# DERIVATION RULE (flag → var): take the long flag, strip the leading `--`,
# uppercase, `-` → `_`, prefix `DS4_DROSTE_`  (e.g. --kv-disk-dir →
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_DISK_DIR). Value flags take the value verbatim; BOOLEAN flags
# take 1/true/yes/on to enable (empty/0/false/no/off = omit the flag).
# EXCEPTION: where ds4 already reads a NATIVE env var for the same knob
# (--threads ↔ DS4_THREADS), the native var is used and there is NO
# DS4_DROSTE_ duplicate — the binary reads natives directly, untranslated.
# Flag list + defaults source-verified against pinned kyuz0/ds4 @00e64ea
# (ds4_server.c parse_options).
#
# NOT listed (use DS4_DROSTE_EXTRA_ARGS if needed): the backend shorthands
# --rocm/--cuda/--metal/--cpu (redundant with DS4_DROSTE_BACKEND) and the
# distributed-run options (--layers etc.; out of single-box scope).

# ── active defaults (droste) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
DS4_DROSTE_HOST=0.0.0.0
DS4_DROSTE_PORT=8000
DS4_DROSTE_KV_DISK_DIR=/opt/data/cache/kv-disk

# ── model ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DS4_DROSTE_MODEL= # REQUIRED — absolute path; easiest: run download_model.sh
#   download_model.sh fetches a curated DeepSeek V4 quant into the shared HF
#   cache and prints the absolute path to paste here.

# ── server flags (uncomment to set; engine defaults shown where fixed) ───────
# DS4_DROSTE_MTP=                     # path to the optional MTP speculative-decoding GGUF
# DS4_DROSTE_MTP_DRAFT=1              # MTP draft tokens
# DS4_DROSTE_MTP_MARGIN=3.0           # MTP acceptance margin
# DS4_DROSTE_CTX=32768                # context size (tokens)
# DS4_DROSTE_TOKENS=393216            # default max tokens per response
# DS4_DROSTE_CHDIR=                   # chdir before serving
# DS4_DROSTE_CORS=                    # boolean — enable CORS
# DS4_DROSTE_TRACE=                   # path — write a request trace file
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_DISK_SPACE_MB=        # cap for the KV disk cache (MB)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_MIN_TOKENS=     # (engine default)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_COLD_MAX_TOKENS=          # (engine default; 0 = unlimited)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_CONTINUED_INTERVAL_TOKENS= # (engine default)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_BOUNDARY_TRIM_TOKENS=     # (engine default)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_BOUNDARY_ALIGN_TOKENS=    # (engine default)
# DS4_DROSTE_KV_CACHE_REJECT_DIFFERENT_QUANT=   # boolean
# DS4_DROSTE_DISABLE_EXACT_DSML_TOOL_REPLAY=    # boolean
# DS4_DROSTE_TOOL_MEMORY_MAX_IDS=100000
# DS4_DROSTE_QUALITY=                 # boolean — quality mode (strict MTP)
# DS4_DROSTE_SSD_STREAMING=           # boolean — stream experts from SSD
# DS4_DROSTE_SSD_STREAMING_COLD=      # boolean
# DS4_DROSTE_SSD_STREAMING_CACHE_EXPERTS=  # positive count or <n>GB
# DS4_DROSTE_SSD_STREAMING_PRELOAD_EXPERTS=  # positive count
# DS4_DROSTE_SIMULATE_USED_MEMORY=    # GiB value, e.g. 64GB
# DS4_DROSTE_PREFILL_CHUNK=           # positive tokens per prefill chunk
# DS4_DROSTE_POWER=                   # 1..100 (percent)
# DS4_DROSTE_DIR_STEERING_FILE=       # directional-steering vector file
# DS4_DROSTE_DIR_STEERING_FFN=        # scale, -100..100
# DS4_DROSTE_DIR_STEERING_ATTN=       # scale, -100..100
# DS4_DROSTE_WARM_WEIGHTS=            # boolean — touch weights at load
# DS4_DROSTE_BACKEND=                 # rocm|cuda|metal|cpu (this image defaults to rocm)

# ── native ds4 env vars (passthrough — the binary reads these itself) ────────
# DS4_THREADS=                        # engine thread count (native ↔ --threads)
# DS4_SERVER_DISABLE_THINK_TOOL_RECOVERY=1
# DS4_MTP_SPEC_DISABLE=1

# ── extra args ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Catch-all appended to the ds4-server command line. Quote the WHOLE value
# (this file is sourced bash); it is then whitespace-split into separate args —
# individual args cannot themselves contain spaces. Example:
#   DS4_DROSTE_EXTRA_ARGS="--warm-weights --prefill-chunk 512"
# DS4_DROSTE_EXTRA_ARGS=
